Login/Signup Scrren
* Tabbar to switch between signup and login
* Signup has 3 textfields for email, password, confirm password
* Clicking sign up takes you to profile setup page
* Login has 2 textfields for email and password
* Clicking login takes you to home page

Profile Setup
* Choose profile pic
* Choose username
* Add a favorite movie/show
* Clicking complete profile brings you to home page

Home Page
* Drop down filter button choices
* Textfield explaining what kind of show you're looking for
* Generate button that prompts AI with your filter/textfield
* Limit of 3 movies/shows displayed with a picture and summary/description

